node.text: In celebration of my @Bet Her Award Nomination for my song #Rooted featuring @EsterDean, I want to Celebrate MY FANS. It was so much fun having some of you in this Viral clip I did with @Thomeography and @Jamaicacraft and some incredible dancers! My Melanin Queens, My Black Queens, All Queens shining! You brought your babies and all! This truly warmed my heart.. I did my part just 2 weeks after giving birth.. I was pushing and having fun! It’s All Rooted in Me. Rooted in You. Rooted in Us! Keep on Dancin’ #StayRooted #Dance

Introducing @LitaByCiara !!!!

From my childhood obsession with my grandmother’s closet in which every item was perfectly tailored to playing dress up in my Mom‘s clothes, and sometimes even my Dad’s...I’ve always had an incredible love for fashion. It’s one of the ways I feel I can best express myself! 
I am so proud to share my Women’s Brand -LITA by Ciara, LITA stands for Love Is The Answer! Women have an incredibly expansive gift for expressing Love. We make a lot happen with our Love. We are empowered by the way we know how to Love. 
I poured a lot of love into every part of the process of creating this line! 
It started with inspiration from vintage and staple pieces in my closet! I’m a High-Low fashion kind of girl, and Tom Boy Chic is my style. 
My goal is for LITA to be your best friend in fashion, your one-stop-shop from day to night. LITA has all your fashion needs covered. 
Join me on this journey! @LitaByCiara #LitaByCiara
